(379, 'c912ac87955289.webp', 'ransform Your Bedroom into a Sleep Oasis\"', 'Creating a Sleep-Friendly Environment: Key Steps for Beating Sleep Deprivation', 'Cozy Bedroom with Soft Lighting and Calming Decor', 'This image illustrates a beautifully designed bedroom with soft, soothing lighting and calming decor elements, creating an ideal sleep-friendly environment. The warm, inviting ambiance of the room is a visual representation of the key steps you can take to beat sleep deprivation. Transform your bedroom into a sleep oasis to ensure a peaceful and restful night\'s sleep, helping you combat sleep deprivation and wake up refreshed.', NULL, '2023-11-02 10:58:21', '2023-11-02 11:09:31'),
(380, '2e47f800f55204.webp', 'Sleep-Boosting Foods to Combat Sleep Deprivation', 'Nutrition and Sleep: Foods like bananas, almonds, and chamomile tea can help alleviate sleep deprivation.', 'Plate of Sleep-Boosting Foods', 'This image features a plate filled with a variety of sleep-enhancing foods, including bananas, almonds, and chamomile tea. These foods are known to have properties that can help alleviate sleep deprivation and promote a good night\'s sleep. Incorporating these nutritious options into your diet may contribute to better sleep quality and overall well-being.', NULL, '2023-11-02 10:58:21', '2023-11-02 11:11:20'),
